title: Green Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Buffet, Salad bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out
description: Buffet spread, choose what you like and pay by weight. Also has assorted beverages and desserts. Ingredients used including quail eggs (vegans beware) , tofu, tempeh, seitan, okara, bulgur, couscous, tahini, and tofuneza (vegan mayonnaise).
